{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_11_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 決して屈しないっ！！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 3.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ない、ない……ここにもない！\nどうしてどこにもないの……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no… not here either!\nWhy can't it be found anywhere…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 333.3333333000006,
          "startTime": 6.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1800.0000715000003,
          "startTime": 7.9000000715
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "マズい、また誰か近づいて来る！\nしかもこの声……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be cafeful‚ someone's approaching again!\nAnd that voices…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.8578234355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "渚と沙季！？\nよりによりって、なんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa and Saki!?\nWhy‚ of all people…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2911567688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "どこか隠れる場所……隠れる場所……！\n{user}さん！　こっちへ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anywhere to hide… a place to hide…!\n{user}-san! This way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4911567688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そっちは観葉植物しかないが\nまさかその後ろに隠れるのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's only a foliage plant over there\nAre you really trying to hide behind this!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.7401590665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それしかないです！　声を出さないでっ、息を潜めて！\nほら、腕を上げて下さい！　枝になりきって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the only option! Don't make a sound‚ hold your breath!\nNow‚ raise your arms! Pretend to be a branch…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2068257332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 30.7401590665
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3859.840933500003,
          "startTime": 34.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5803.8121859,
          "startTime": 36.5439712524
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無茶を言うな！　くっ、だがやるしかないか\nう、腕を枝のようにしならせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's ridculous order! Ugh‚ but I have to do it\nUm‚ stretch out arms like branches",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 41.8068257332
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5326.507600100002,
          "startTime": 47.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8093.174266799999,
          "startTime": 49.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9993.174266799997,
          "startTime": 51.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9211.564045899997,
          "startTime": 51.0183897791
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.6850564321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "行った……？ 　ふふ、全然気付いてませんでしたね\n私達、完璧な演技でしたよ……！　完全に枝でした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're gone…? Fufu‚ They didn't seem to notice at all\nWem acted perfectly…! We were totally branches!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3850564321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8066.666666700002,
          "startTime": 59.7517230988
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10848.276901200003,
          "startTime": 62.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "単に二人が見向きもしなかったからだよ\n話に夢中な様子だったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that they didn't look at us\nThey seemed engrossed in their conversation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3356460889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、助かりましたね。本当にひやひやしました\nただ、これだけ探しても鍵が見つからないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ we were saved. I was really nervous\nHowever‚ even after searching so much‚ I still couldn't find the key…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8023127556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1356460889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、このままだと{user}さんと\n一生繋がれたまま……ご飯の時も、ね、寝る時も！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-At this rate‚ {user}-san and I will be handcuffed\nfor the rest of our lives… even when we eat‚ and even when we sleep!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3023127556,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2166.666666699996,
          "startTime": 85.3023127556
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6864.353911099996,
          "startTime": 90
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、さすがにそうなったら鍵の業者を……？\nなぁ、今気付いたんだが、この手錠のボタンはなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ if that happens‚ I'll have to call a locksmith…?\nHey‚ I just noticed‚ what's this button on the handcuffs?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6706137975,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7397.687244400004,
          "startTime": 99
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6825393041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なんでしょうかこれ……\n「アンロック」って書いて――っ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What is this…\nIt says 'Unlock'―― Huh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7648229086,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6517.460695899998,
          "startTime": 109.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7784.127362599989,
          "startTime": 110.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7784.127362599989,
          "startTime": 110.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "外れた……！　押しただけで、こんな簡単に……\nよ、良かったぁ～！　ほら、外れましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It came off…! Just by pressing it‚ so easily…\nT-Thank goodness~! See‚ it's off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9825362524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9825362524
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2158695858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もともと鍵なんてなかったのか\nはぁ～……本当に安心したよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was no key in the first place\nHaa~… I'm so relieved…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0999969483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3500645638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、本当に……ふふふっ、すみません、ご迷惑を\nおかけしちゃったのに、さすがにおかしくって、ふふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ really… Fufufu‚ sorry‚ even though I\ncaused trouble‚ it was still strange‚ fufufu",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8167312305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに見つからないよう隠れるなんて、潜入捜査する\n警察官みたいだったな。とんだハプニングだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hiding from everyone trying to avoid being discovered‚ I felt like\na police officer on an undercover investigation. It was a unfortunate happening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2999969483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of filming",
        "id": ""
